1. General
     Show scroll bars: Always

2. Desktop & Screen Saver
     Screen Saver
       Start after: 30 Minutes

3. Dock & Menu Bar
     Dock
       Position on screen: Left
       Automatically hide and show the Dock: Yes
       Show recent applications in Dock: No
     Menu Bar
       Automatically hide and show the menu bar: Yes
     Bluetooth
       Show in Menu Bar: Yes
     AirDrop
       Show in Menu Bar: Yes
     Clock
       Show the day of the week: No
       Show date: No
       Show AM/PM: No
 
4. Mission Control
     Hot corners
       Top left: Mission Control
       Top right: Application Windows
       Bottom right: Desktop
       Bottom left: Launchpad

5. Keyboard
     Text
       Capitalize words automatically: No

6. Energy Saver
     Turn display off after: Never
     Prevent computer from sleeping automatically when the display is off: Yes
     Put hard disks to sleep when possible: No
     Start up automatically after a power failure: Yes

7. Sharing
     File Sharing: On
     Options
       Windows File Sharing: On

